milestones.description: Kevin Sandher and Codrington's 30-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Codrington and Ashish Patel
Codrington and Henry Osinde's 36-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Seebaran and Ashish Patel
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for CAN, going past John Davison

stories.title: Minors steers Bermuda to victory
stories.subTitle: Bermuda v Canada, Tri-Nation ODI, Trinidad
stories.summary: A gutsy unbeaten 46 from wicketkeeper Dean Minors guided Bermuda to a three-wicket victory over Canada in a game they appeared to have thrown away at Queen's Park Oval in Trinidad
